en_8646231_0	COLOMBO (News 1st) – A 22 year old Indian national in possession of 500g of “ICE” worth Rs.
en_8646231_1	5.8 million has been taken into custody by the officials of the Police Narcotics Bureau attached to the Bandaranaike International Airport.
en_8646231_2	The suspect had arrived in the country from Chennai, India. The narcotics were found concealed in his luggage.
en_8646231_3	Following the standing order issued by the Negombo Magistrate Court today (October 01) the suspect is due to be produced before the Police Narcotics Bureau for further investigations.
